snippet.title: Destiny: Rising | Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
PRE-REGISTRATION IS NOW OPEN for Destiny: Rising, the very first Mobile Epic Sci-Fi RPG Shooter set in an alternate Destiny timeline. 

*ALL FOOTAGE IS TAKEN FROM EARLY PRE-ALPHA MOBILE IN-GAME CAPTURE.

Enter an era of heroes and legends, fight with their unique super abilities and weaponry, and secure humanity's future.

The first closed alpha kicks off in November. Pre-register now for a chance to join! https://bit.ly/3Y4tz6z

Closed Alpha Test info: http://spr.ly/6003q6nCS

Follow us and join us on:
X: https://x.com/_DestinyRising
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PlayDestinyRising
Discord: https://discord.gg/destinyrising
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playdestinyrising/
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@playdestinyrising

#DestinyRising #Mobile #Destiny
